videos.description: On the fast break, Hurricanes' Chris Lykes drives but Wolfpack's Markell Johnson swats away his lay-in attempt.
videos.headline: NC State's Johnson skies for a block

videos.description: Miami's Chris Lykes soars up to deny a lay-in attempt and Lonnie Walker IV slams it home on the fast break.
videos.headline: Lykes' block leads to Walker dunk

videos.description: Lonnie Walker IV goes in for a layup, but Wolfpack's 7-foot center Omer Yurtseven swats the ball away.
videos.headline: Canes' Walker denied at the rim

videos.description: Omer Yurtseven receives the pass under the basket and flushes it in with a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: NCSU's Yurtseven finishes with a jam

videos.description: Ebuka Izundu hammers it home and the ball bounces off his knee and it goes back up through the basket.
videos.headline: Miami's Izundu dunks, knees ball back through hoop

videos.description: Bruce Brown Jr. throws down a one-handed hammer in transition.
videos.headline: Hurricanes' Brown finishes with monster slam

videos.description: Hurricanes' Bruce Brown Jr. weaves through two defenders and lays it in.
videos.headline: Miami's Brown splits D for layup
